Ugly Drum Smoker.

Using the second donated oil drum the plan is to convert it into an ugly drum smoker.

Resources:
1 Large 55 gallon oil drum.
Angle grinder with a cutting and wire brush head.
Power Hose.
Welder.
Drill.
Pipes.
Steel caster wheels.
valves.
Grates.
Wire mesh.
Heat resistant paint.
Decals.

